{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"플렉스박스","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Flexbox","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>플렉스박스</strong>(Flexbox)는 요소를 단일 차원(행 또는 열)에 배치하는 레이아웃 모델인 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Flexible Box Layout Module</a>을 부를 때 흔히 사용하는 이름입니다.</p>\n<p>명세는 플렉스박스를 사용자 인터페이스 디자인을 위한 레이아웃 모델로 설명하고 있습니다. 플렉스박스의 주요 기능은 플렉스 레이아웃 내의 각 항목이 커지거나 작아질 수 있다는 점입니다. 여백은 항목에 포함할 수도 있고, 각 항목의 사이에 분배할 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p>또한 플렉스박스는 항목의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Main_Axis\">주축</a> 및 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Cross_Axis\">교차축</a> 정렬을 가능케 하여 다수의 항목에 대한 정렬 및 크기의 고수준 통제를 제공합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_알아보기","title":"더 알아보기","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"속성_참고서","title":"속성 참고서","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/align-content\"><code>align-content</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-items\"><code>align-items</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-self\"><code>align-self</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex\"><code>flex</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-basis\"><code>flex-basis</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-flow\"><code>flex-flow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-grow\"><code>flex-grow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-shrink\"><code>flex-shrink</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-wrap\"><code>flex-wrap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content\"><code>justify-content</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/order\"><code>order</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_읽어보기","title":"더 읽어보기","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><em><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Flexible Box Layout Module Level 1 Specification</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Flexbox\">Basic Concepts of Flexbox</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Relationship_of_Flexbox_to_Other_Layout_Methods\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Relationship of flexbox to other layout methods (en-US)</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Aligning_Items_in_a_Flex_Container\">Aligning items in a flex container</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Ordering_Flex_Items\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Ordering flex items (en-US)</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Controlling_Ratios_of_Flex_Items_Along_the_Main_Ax\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Controlling Ratios of flex items along the main axis (en-US)</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Mastering_Wrapping_of_Flex_Items\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Mastering wrapping of flex items (en-US)</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Typical_Use_Cases_of_Flexbox\">Typical use cases of flexbox</a></em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"더 알아보기","id":"더_알아보기"}],"summary":"플렉스박스(Flexbox)는 요소를 단일 차원(행 또는 열)에 배치하는 레이아웃 모델인 CSS Flexible Box Layout Module을 부를 때 흔히 사용하는 이름입니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Flexbox (フレックスボックス)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Flexbox","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/glossary/flexbox","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/glossary/flexbox/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary","title":"용어 사전"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Flexbox","title":"플렉스박스"}],"pageTitle":"플렉스박스 - 용어 사전 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}